[I] Digital camera support for KDE

[T] Picture Transfer Protocol (PTP) is an older method of talking to camera
[T] devices. Kamera provides a configuration tool and a KIO worker to read and
[T] write to camera devices with this protocol.

[U] https://apps.kde.org/kamera/

